  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;The proposal by reason of its scale, siting and design is considered to&amp;nbsp;result in an unacceptable detrimental impact upon the amenity of neighbouring occupiers in terms of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:14.6667px&quot;&gt;loss of privacy, increased sense of enclosure and loss of outlook together with increased noise and disturbance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt; contrary to Policy LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020)&amp;nbsp;and Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:11pt&quot;&gt;The proposed roof terrace by virtue of its&amp;nbsp;siting and design&amp;nbsp;result in an incongruous and incompatible form of development which would fail to relate to the character and appearance of the existing host building&amp;nbsp;and other buildings in the terrace.&amp;nbsp;As such, the proposal would be contrary to Policy D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) of the London Plan (2021) and&amp;nbsp;Policy&amp;nbsp;LP1 (Design qualities and local character) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020)&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;the Hackney Residential&amp;nbsp;Extensions and Alterations SPD 2009.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
